### Pagination API Examples

# Basic pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=5

# Sort by creation date (newest first)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&sort=created_at desc

# Sort by start date ascending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&sort=start_date asc

# Filter by destination city (case-insensitive)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&destination_city=ilike jakarta

# Search in activity purpose
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&activity_purpose=ilike meeting

# Filter by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&start_date=gte 2024-01-01&end_date=lte 2024-12-31

# Multiple filters with sorting
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=15&sort=created_at desc&destination_city=ilike jakarta&activity_purpose=ilike client

# Filter by multiple cities
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&destination_city=in Jakarta,Surabaya,Bandung

# Complex multi-field sorting
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=20&sort=destination_city asc,start_date desc

# Recent trips (last 30 days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&created_at=gte 2024-10-18

# Exclude specific destinations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&destination_city=nin Jakarta,Bandung

# Exact match filtering
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/business-trips?page=1&limit=10&destination_city=eq Jakarta